* 719 CE (Yōrō 3): Appointed Inspector of {{ill|Aki Province|ja|安芸国}} and {{ill|Suo Province|ja|周防国}}; served as Governor of {{ill|Bizen Province|ja|備前国}}
* 720 CE (Yōrō 4): Promoted to {{ill|Shogo-i no Jō|ja|正五位上|1=Senior Fifth Rank|lt=Senior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade}}
* 724 CE (Shinki 1): Promoted to {{ill|Jushi-i|ja|従四位下|lt=Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|1=Junior Fourth Rank}}
* Date unknown: Held the post of {{ill|Benkan (Magistrate)|ja|弁官|lt=Benkan}} (Right Major Controller)

