* 719 CE (Yōrō 3): Appointed Inspector of {{ill|Aki Province|ja|安芸国|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Aki Province|qq=}} and {{ill|Suo Province|ja|周防国|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suo Province|qq=}}; served as Governor of {{ill|Bizen Province|ja|備前国|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bizen Province|qq=}}
* 720 CE (Yōrō 4): Promoted to {{ill|Shogo-i no Jō|ja|正五位上|1=Senior Fifth Rank|lt=Senior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shogo-i no Jō|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Fifth Rank|qq=}}
* 724 CE (Shinki 1): Promoted to {{ill|Jushi-i|ja|従四位下|lt=Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|1=Junior Fourth Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jushi-i|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fourth Rank|qq=}}
* Date unknown: Held the post of {{ill|Benkan (Magistrate)|ja|弁官|1=Benkan (administrator)|lt=Benkan|lt=Benkan|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Benkan (Magistrate)|qq=}} (Right Major Controller)

